A set of sample plot commands for python UEDGE
*********************************************************

First, within a ipython-uedge session, type
from uedgeplots import *

Then you can plot many profiles, for example:

=======
Plotting profiles on outer divertor plate:
=======

profile(com.yyrb,bbb.ne[com.nx,],title=“Electron density”, ylabel=“Distance along outer plate (m)”, xlabel=“ne (1/m**3)”)

profile(com.yyrb,bbb.ng[com.nx,],title=“Hydrogen atom density”, ylabel=“Distance along outer plate (m)”, xlabel=“ng(1/m**3)”)

profile(com.yyrb,bbb.te[com.nx,]/bbb.ev,title=“Electron temperature”, ylabel=“Distance along outer plate (m)”, xlabel=“Te (eV)”)

profile(com.yyrb,bbb.ti[com.nx,]/bbb.ev,title=“Ion temperature”, ylabel=“Distance along outer plate (m)”, xlabel=“Ti (eV)”)

profile(com.yyrb,bbb.feex[com.nx,],title=“Electron thermal heat flux *area”, ylabel=“Distance along outer plate (m)”, xlabel=“feex”)

profile(com.yyrb,bbb.feix[com.nx,],title=“Ion thermal heat flux *area”, ylabel=“Distance along outer plate (m)”, xlabel=“feix”)


=======
Plotting profiles on inner divertor plate:
=======

profile(com.yylb,bbb.ne[0,],title=“Electron density”, ylabel=“Distance along inner plate (m)”, xlabel=“ne (1/m**3)”)

profile(com.yylb,bbb.ng[0,],title=“Hydrogen atom density”, ylabel=“Distance along inner plate (m)”, xlabel=“ng(1/m**3)”)

profile(com.yylb,bbb.te[0,]/bbb.ev,title=“Electron temperature”, ylabel=“Distance along inner plate (m)”, xlabel=“Te (eV)”)

profile(com.yylb,bbb.ti[0,]/bbb.ev,title=“Ion temperature”, ylabel=“Distance along inner plate (m)”, xlabel=“Ti (eV)”)

profile(com.yylb,-bbb.feex[0,],title=“Electron thermal heat flux *area”, ylabel=“Distance along inner plate (m)”, xlabel=“feex”)

profile(com.yylb,-bbb.feix[0,],title=“Ion thermal heat flux *area”, ylabel=“Distance along inner plate (m)”, xlabel=“feix”)

=======
Plotting midplane profiles:
=======

profile(com.yylb,bbb.ne[bbb.ixmp,],title=“Electron density at midplane”, ylabel=“Distance from separatrix (m)”, xlabel=“ne (1/m**3)”)

profile(com.yylb,bbb.ng[bbb.ixmp,],title=“Hydrogen atom density at midplane”, ylabel=“Distance from separatrix (m)”, xlabel=“ng(1/m**3)”)

profile(com.yylb,bbb.te[bbb.ixmp,]/bbb.ev,title=“Electron temperature at midplane”, ylabel=“Distance from separatrix (m)”, xlabel=“Te (eV)”)

profile(com.yylb,bbb.ti[bbb.ixmp,]/bbb.ev,title=“Ion temperature at midplane”, ylabel=“Distance from separatrix (m)”, xlabel=“Ti (eV)”)



